---
// Features section
---

<section id="features" class="py-20 bg-muted/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        Everything You Need for 
        <span class="gradient-text">Modern Ham Radio</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Professional-grade features designed for the modern ham operator, 
        built with cutting-edge web technologies.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Radio Control -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Complete Radio Control</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Full frequency, mode, power, and VFO control with real-time feedback and band presets.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• Frequency control with band presets</li>
          <li>• All radio modes (LSB, USB, CW, AM, FM, Digital)</li>
          <li>• Power control with safety warnings</li>
          <li>• VFO A/B switching and split operation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Spectrum Analyzer -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Advanced Spectrum Analyzer</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Real-time FFT spectrum analysis with waterfall display and professional controls.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• WebGL-accelerated rendering</li>
          <li>• Combined spectrum + waterfall view</li>
          <li>• Auto-detect best data source (IF/IQ/PCM)</li>
          <li>• Fullscreen modal with advanced controls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Audio System -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072m2.828-9.9a9 9 0 010 12.728M5.586 15H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h1.586l4.707-4.707C10.923 3.663 12 4.109 12 5v14c0 .891-1.077 1.337-1.707.707L5.586 15z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Professional Audio</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Dual audio routing with device management, processing, and real-time level meters.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• Separate radio and computer audio</li>
          <li>• Device enumeration and selection</li>
          <li>• Noise reduction and compression</li>
          <li>• Real-time level meters with peak hold</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Cross-Platform -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Cross-Network Support</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Run frontend on laptop while backend operates on Raspberry Pi for optimal setup.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• Frontend on laptop, backend on Pi</li>
          <li>• Automatic network discovery</li>
          <li>• Dynamic backend URL configuration</li>
          <li>• Real-time WebSocket communication</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Modern UX -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Modern UX Design</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Clean, responsive interface with dark/light themes and professional ham radio aesthetics.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• Dark and light theme support</li>
          <li>• Responsive design for all devices</li>
          <li>• Professional color palette</li>
          <li>• Intuitive navigation and controls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Open Source -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Open Source & Free</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          MIT licensed, community-driven development with comprehensive documentation.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
          <li>• MIT License - completely free</li>
          <li>• Active community development</li>
          <li>• Comprehensive documentation</li>
          <li>• Easy to contribute and extend</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
